Due persone sono morte e decine sono rimaste ferite a causa di una serie di #tornado che ha colpito ieri gli Stati del #Wisconsin e dell'#Oklahoma.
Una delle vittime si trovava in un campo caravan nel Wisconsin, dove sono rimaste ferite oltre 25 persone. L'altra vittima e' stata segnala a #ElkCity, in Oklahoma, circa 180 chilometri a ovest di Oklahoma City.
Il servizio meteorologico statunitense ha ricevuto oltre due dozzine di segnalazioni di tornado in cinque Stati: #Texas, Oklahoma, #Kansas, #Nebraska e Wisconsin.

FINISHED. "82:58" ●Faber-Castell Pitt Pen (XS) 4 pens total.
●Borden Riley Paris Paper.
●82 hrs 58 minutes to completion over the course of 32 days.
●Available for purchase.

Just in case you were wondering, I did *not* feel the urge to spend another 2 minutes on this piece to round out the time I have invested! 
This piece was a beautiful practice in patience and determination. 
I will get this framed just as soon as I can. I cannot wait to see it properly displayed and in daylight! I will share better quality pictures! 
Thank you to all who have encouraged me and cheered me on. Thank you for following me for this past month as I worked! I look forward to my next creation after a few days break, if I can last that long without drawing!
